%N A103133 Decimal expansion of Dirichlet series L_{-7}(2).
%H A103133 D. Cvijovic, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1011.0195">Proof of the Borwein-Broadhurst conjecture for a dilogarithmic integral arising in quantum field theory</a>, arXiv:1011.0195 [math-ph], 2010.
